# ⚠️ IMPORTANT: reemplace accessToken to a valid one before doing the test
@accessToken = {{accessToken}}

### Get all users

GET {{host}}/api/users
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Get user by id

GET {{host}}/api/users/4
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

